         foreground background
M_BLACK        30         40
M_M_RED          31         41
M_GREEN        32         42
M_YELLOW       33         43
blue         34         44
magenta      35         45
M_M_CYAN         36         46
white        37         47
Additionally, you can use these:

M_M_RESET             0  (everything back to normal)
bold/bright       1  (often a brighter shade of the same colour)
underline         4
inverse           7  (swap foreground and background colours)
bold/bright off  21
underline off    24
inverse off      27